[Name] Uswsusp
[Summary] Userspace software suspend utility
[License] GPL2 (or later)
[Description] Uswsusp (aka µswsusp or suspend) contains the tools to \
use the userspace software suspend functions available in Linux 2.6.17 \
and later. It supports two modes, suspend-to-disk (also called \
hibernation) and suspend-to-ram. Uswsusp also supports encryption of \
the snapshot and themable splash.
[Homepage] https://suspend.sourceforge.net/